metadata.Description: The Sun The person lives for a long time and becomes wealthy. He will have wife children and many servants. He gets royal and governmental favours and achieves success without much effort. He will be sagacious and principled.

metadata.Name: MoonInHouse11
metadata.Description: The Moon One will be noble generous and blessed with riches wife and children. Introspective by nature and quiet-going he will become famous making good profits in business. He will acquire vast lands and be helped in his endeavours by the fair sex.

metadata.Name: MarsInHouse11
metadata.Description: Mars - The native will be an eloquent and forceful speaker clever and rich but lustful will acquire landed Properties and wield considerable influence in top circles.

metadata.Name: MercuryInHouse11
metadata.Description: MercuryOne becomes learned in many sciences. He will possess a keen and sharp intellect will be wealthy truthful and happy will have many faithful servants and will prosper in engineering ventures.

metadata.Name: JupiterInHouse11
metadata.Description: JupiterThe native will be long-lived. He will have a limited number of issues will be bold and wealthy with a piercing intellect and will become renowned. He will be fond of music will accumulate riches and will have many friends.

metadata.Name: VenusInHouse11
metadata.Description: Venus  He will be of a wandering nature will make immense profits possessing all kinds of comforts and luxuries. He will have a weakness for women and long for their company. He will be popular having many friends.

metadata.Name: SaturnInHouse11
metadata.Description: Saturn The native earns through employing many men and women. He will have few friends will be fond of enjoyment and will earn through Government sources. He will have a long and healthy life and will be involved in politics commanding great respect.

metadata.Name: RahuInHouse11
metadata.Description: Rahu -The native distinguishes himself in the army or navy will become famous wealthy and learned  will have few children will suffer from ear afflictions and will earn much wealth in foreign countries.

metadata.Name: KetuInHouse11
metadata.Description: Ketu The native will have the habit of hoarding. He may get monetary wind-fall through speculation such as lottery horse-racing and the stock exchange. Noble and possessed of many good qualities of head and heart he will succeed in all his ventures and will participate in charitable and similar works of beneficence.

metadata.Name: SunInHouse12
metadata.Description: The Sun The native may take to an immoral life and engage himself in vile occupations. He will not be quite successful in his life and may feel neglected by all. He will suffer the loss of some limb and have weak eye-sight. He will however be energetic and have sons.

metadata.Name: MoonInHouse12
metadata.Description: The Moon  The native may suffer from some deformity. He will be narrow-minded hard-hearted and mischievous. He prefers to lead on obscure life in solitude. Eye-sight will be weak. If the Moon is waning and combines with Saturn sloth and lethargy will be the result.

metadata.Name: MarsInHouse12
metadata.Description: Mars  The person may lose his wife. He will be selfish hateful and suffer diseases due to excess of heat in the body. He is liable to deception and may lose his money. If Mars and Saturn occupy the 12th and the 2nd houses respectively the Moon be in Lagna and the Sun in the 7th house he may suffer from leucoderma. If Mars in the 12th house is aspected by the Sun danger from fire and wicked people is indicated. Malefics in the 7th and the 8th and Mars in the 12th denote that one will have another wife even when the first is alive.

metadata.Name: MercuryInHouse12
metadata.Description: Mercury Capricious and wayward the person will indulge in extra-marital relations and suffer penury and perverted thinking will make him unhappy. He will also have a few children.

metadata.Name: JupiterInHouse12
metadata.Description: Jupiter The native may deride religion and be evil-minded. He will commit fearful deeds and lead a lascivious life. Later on he repents and reforms himself. The native will always be anxious about his vehicles ornaments and clothes.

metadata.Name: VenusInHouse12
metadata.Description: Venus  Desertion by relatives  hankering after comforts without success and penury will make the natives life miserable. He will indulge in lying and associates with low women. His eye-sight will be poor. If Venus is exalted contrary results will happen.

metadata.Name: SaturnInHouse12
metadata.Description: Saturn  The native will be dull-headed and lose all his money. He will have squint eyes and a deformed limb make many enemies suffer losses in trade be a pessimist and commits sins in secret.

metadata.Name: RahuInHouse12
metadata.Description: Rahu  The native will be prosperous immoral but of a helpful nature. He will have eye troubles. If the Sun is in the 7th Mars is in the 10th and Rahu is in the 12th Bhava the natives father will die early.

metadata.Name: KetuInHouse12
metadata.Description: Ketu  The native will have a restless and wandering mind and leave his country of birth. The lower classes will befriend him. All his inherited property may be lost.

metadata.Name: GeminiRisingWithEvilPlanet
metadata.Description: Evil planets are in Gemini trickery and deceit will characterize their nature.

metadata.Name: AriesRisingWithEvilPlanet
metadata.Description: Mental affliction and derangement are also likely since Saturn and the Moon are in Aries.

metadata.Name: Lord2WithEvilInHouse
metadata.Description: If the second lord is in the 2nd with evil planets or aspected by him he will be poor.

metadata.Name: SaturnIn2WithVenus
metadata.Description: Ordinary wealth is indicated if Saturn is in the 2nd aspected by Venus.

metadata.Name: MoonMarsIn2WithSaturnAspect
metadata.Description: If the Moon and Mars reside in the 2nd bhava and Saturn aspects it he suffers from a peculiar skin disease.

metadata.Name: MercuryAndEvilIn2WithMoonAspect
metadata.Description: The situation of Mercury in the 2nd with another evil planet aspected by the Moon is bad for saving money. Even if there is any ancestral wealth it will be spentrather wasted on extravagant purposes.

metadata.Name: SunIn2WithNoSaturnAspect
metadata.Description: The Sun in the 2nd without being aspected by Saturn is favorable for a steady fortune.

metadata.Name: MoonIn2WithMercuryAspect
metadata.Description: The Moon being placed in the 2nd and aspected by Mercury is favorable for earning money by self-exertion.

metadata.Name: Lord2And3In6WithEvilPlanet
metadata.Description: He will be poor if lords of the 2nd and 3rd are in the 6th with or aspected by evil planets.

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse1
metadata.Description: If the second lord is in the first  One earns money by his own exertions and generally by manual labour. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse1AndLord1InHouse2
metadata.Description: In the second  Riches will be acquired without effort if the 1st and 2nd lords have exchanged their houses. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse3
metadata.Description: In the third  Loss from relatives brothers and gain from travels and journeys. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse4
metadata.Description: In the fourth - Through mother inheritance. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse5
metadata.Description: In the fifth  Ancestral properties speculation and chance games. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse6
metadata.Description: In the sixth  Brokers business loss from relatives. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse7
metadata.Description: In the seventh  Gain after marriage but loss from sickness etc. of wife. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse8
metadata.Description: In the eighth  Legacies and enemies. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse9
metadata.Description: In the ninth  From father voyages and shipping. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse10
metadata.Description: In the tenth  Profession eminent people government favours. source of income

metadata.Name: Lord2InHouse11
metadata.Description: In the eleventh  From different means. source of income

metadata.Name: MaleficIn11FromArudha
metadata.Description: Unjust means of earning because malefic planets in the 11th from Arudha Lagna.

metadata.Name: BeneficIn11FromArudha
metadata.Description: Just means of earning because benefic planets in the 11th from Arudha Lagna.

metadata.Name: MarsVenusIn7th
metadata.Description: When Mars and Venus are in the 7th the boy or girl concerned will have strong sex instincts and such an individual should be mated to one who has similar instincts

metadata.Name: MercuryOrJupiterIn7th
metadata.Description: Mercury or Jupiter in the 7th makes one under-sexed. And such an individual should not be mated to a person with strong sex instincts.

metadata.Name: LeoLagna7thLordSaturnIn2
metadata.Description: When Leo is Lagna and the 7th lord Saturn is in the 2nd the husband will be subservient to the wife carrying out all her orders.

metadata.Name: SaturnIn7thNotLagnaLord
metadata.Description: Saturn in the 7th house is also indicative of unhappiness in marriage unless Saturn happens to be either lord of Lagna or lord of the 7th. exception accounted for

metadata.Name: MarsIn7thNoBenefics
metadata.Description: If Kuja is in the 7th house unaspected or not joined by benefics there will be frequent quarrels in the married life often leading to misunderstandings and separation.

metadata.Name: SunVenusIn5th7th9th
metadata.Description: If the Sun and Venus occupy the 5th 7th or 9th house then the native will lack marital happiness.

metadata.Name: Lord7And1Friends
metadata.Description: Lords of the 7th and 1st are friends then the native will be loved by his wife.

metadata.Name: Lord7And1NotFriends
metadata.Description: Lords of the 7th and 1st are enemies or bitter enemies. There will be no harmony in marriage.

metadata.Name: SaturnIn7th
metadata.Description: Saturn in the 7th confers stability in the marriage but the husband or wife manifests coldness and not warmth.
